T02D3356:37a-1: sam kshipta pradzny'a p'a ra mi ta s'a dha nam /
T02D3356:37a-3: mdor bsdus pa'i shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma'i sgrub thabs /
T02D3356:37a-4: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3356:37a-5: sngon du bstan pa'i cho gas stong pa nyid bsgoms
T02D3356:37a-6: pa'i rjes su padma dmar po dang zla ba la
T02D3356:37a-7: gnas pa'i dh'i:ser po yongs su gyur pa las /
T02D3356:37a-8: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma ser mo /
T02D3356:37a-9: mi bskyod pa dbus su gnas pa'i ral pa'i cod pan can ma /
T02D3356:37b-1: po ti dang bcas pa'i autpa la sngon po g-yon logs su 'dzin ma /
T02D3356:37b-3: na bza' dmar pos brgyan ma zhes bya ba /
T02D3356:37b-5: aom dh'i:shru ti smri ti bi dza ye sv'a h'a /
T02D3356:37b-6: zhes bya ba'i sngags bzlas pa'o //
T02D3356:37b-7: mdor bsdus pa'i shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so //
T02D3356:37b-8: pandi ta don yod rdo rje dang /
